channel.title: [Optimized] DeltaClean [Clean]
channel.description:
[center][font=Verdana][size=25pt]DELTACLEAN[/size][/font][/center]
Because no matter how hard people try, Everybody still uses DeltaScape, and because its mainly in experienced programmars who use it, i thought we might aswell have them starting with this, to learn conventions and work with cleaner code
So what i've done is quickly whip this up.
[size=20pt]Notable Features[/size]
- Everything DeltaScape has - Grahams EventManager - Full Indentation across all classes - Removed over 1000 dead code fragments - Follows 100% Convention across classes (Except for the basic packaging + method names(way to many to refactor)) - Has multiple notorious Delta-Bugs Fixed - Runs ALOT smoother then regular DeltaScape - Has tips and guides on how to edit basic things for beginners - Works with most clients (Galkons refactored etc) - Will hold atleast 30% more players then an average DeltaScape - Alot more - Download and look.
[size=20pt]THIS HAS EVERY IN GAME FEATURE DELTA HAS IT IS JUST ALOT CLEANER CODE & RUNS BETTER - IT IS DELTASCAPE I WONT POST PICTURES[/size]
Just for the record, I, in no way support the use of DeltaScape but if people insist on using it, they might aswell use this version of it so they learn some basic fundamentals.
Download Link : http://uppit.com/v/8hk5nrz3
Rep is appreciated
Credits -
Teh Jonny J Graham Delta_ Java' Blakeman6092 *balla*
Anybody else who wants some
Please Download & look @ source before commenting, this is the best cleaned version of it by far.
